Few days back i went to People Square located at burns road for @jeelo.dobara campaign their initiative is to make people vaccinated.
There were 2 dustbins ,1 with a happy mood emoji and other 1 with sad mood emoji. People who were vaccinated were throwing their rubbish in happy face bins and those who were not vaccinated were throwing in sad face bins. I was so happy to see the positive response of the people because they are vaccinated 😍
